# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment Variables (Module 23 — Build & Deploy)
#
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to .env
# 2. Fill in your own TMDB API key (get one free at https://www.themoviedb.org)
# 3. NEVER commit the real .env file to Git — it's in .gitignore
# 4. In Vite, variables MUST start with VITE_ to be available in the browser
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_TMDB_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
VITE_TMDB_BASE_URL=https://api.themoviedb.org/3
VITE_TMDB_IMAGE_BASE_URL=https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500
